Overview

This dashboard shows Host overview related to the Prisma Cloud Integration.

The dashboard is made to provide general statistics and show the detection of the ingested hosts from Prisma Cloud.

It displays total count of hosts. Also shows the distribution of hosts by agentless scanner, package type, package name, type, application name and OS. Details regarding compliance issues and distribution, and vulnerability distribution are also shown. Saved Search of Cloud metadata essential details is also displayed.
It fetches new updates every 1 minute by default.
